data.description: Come check out this GREAT house in Santa Rita! It has large windows providing an abundance of natural light. There is a large, open concept entertaining space with a huge deck in the backyard. This house backs up to the park and is walking distance from the elementary school. The bathrooms have been recently remodeled and it has beautiful hardwood floors throughout. There is a bonus space separate from the house with central heat/air and an exterior lock, perfect for storage!
